Subject: [T2] Flywheel torque

I always use a line of Blue locktite on the flywheel bolts. Clean the bolts 
with brake cleaner, let dry, put a line of Blue Locktite about 1 eighth wide 
( no wider ) let dry completely. lubricate sparcely, install in progressive 
torque asymetrical pattern.  Cree
